      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be verified and version-controlled per MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R1 was used under a validated SQA plan; version control and regression testing logs confirm compliance with MRL 2 SQA requirements."
    },
    {
