      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., normalized index of hemolysis) must be reported between simulation and experimental outputs.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) predicted by CFD agrees with experimental measurements within 15% across all operating points tested, meeting MRL 2 output comparison criteria."
